## **2. Immutable Financial Logic (Blockchain-Inspired)**

### Best Practice Applied:
```javascript
// Immutable charity allocation
const CHARITY_LOCK = Object.freeze({
  profitAllocation: 0.45,  // 45% locked
  vipGiftAllocation: 0.02, // 2% locked
  friendsSecurity: 0.01,   // 1% locked
  immutable: true
});

// Cannot be modified even by admin
Object.seal(CHARITY_LOCK);
```

**Why World-Class:**
- ‚úÖ **Transparency**: All transactions auditable
- ‚úÖ **Trust**: Code-enforced charity commitments
- ‚úÖ **Security**: No human can alter core financial rules
- ‚úÖ **Compliance**: Meets global financial regulations

