## **4. AI-Powered Security (Purity Shield)**

### Best Practice Applied:
```python
# Multi-layer threat detection
class PurityShield:
    def scan_content(self, content):
        threats = []
        
        # Layer 1: Profanity detection
        if self.detect_profanity(content):
            threats.append("PROFANITY")
        
        # Layer 2: Fraud detection
        if self.detect_fraud(content):
            threats.append("FRAUD")
        
        # Layer 3: Spam detection
        if self.detect_spam(content):
            threats.append("SPAM")
        
        return self.take_action(threats)
```

**Why World-Class:**
- ‚úÖ **Proactive Defense**: Prevents attacks before they happen
- ‚úÖ **Machine Learning**: Improves over time
- ‚úÖ **Zero-Trust Model**: Verify everything
- ‚úÖ **Automated Response**: No manual intervention needed

---

## **5. Modular & Extensible Design**

### Best Practice Applied:
```javascript
// Plugin architecture
class MuqaddasCore {
  constructor() {
    this.modules = new Map();
  }
  
  registerModule(name, module) {
    this.modules.set(name, module);
  }
  
  // Easy to add new features
  addFeature(feature) {
    this.modules.get('features').add(feature);
  }
}
```

**Why World-Class:**
- ‚úÖ **Extensibility**: Add 500+ apps without core changes
- ‚úÖ **Maintainability**: Each module independent
- ‚úÖ **Testability**: Unit test each component
- ‚úÖ **Reusability**: Modules shareable across projects

